{"tid":1020703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真人真事 入黎睇下 琴日去左荃灣大窩口間網吧打機 有人唔記得登出LoL帳號😂","createTime":"2019-02-13T19:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T03:56:19.000Z","uid":183394,"like":20,"dislike":835,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"e33702860ccfab7465f9a5093f3d04ec7e16acd5","tid":1020703,"uid":183394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T19:24:19.000Z","msg":"件事就咁既 我琴晚同個fd去網吧打機 坐低左入埋自己會員 之後見到入面有個未登出既LoL帳戶 之後順便幫佢用5場 用劫上專7😂<br />\n（呢間網吧好特別 如果部電腦登出左 但唔係關機既話 300秒內自己關機之前 第二條友入到會員 佢都當繼續挽 因為廢事D人唔記得加鐘 所以登出左有300秒既限制）<br />\n重點呢 之後佢Ac入面有個好友 無啦啦搵佢挽<br />\n（即係我）咁好啦 我同埋我個fd一齊挽 <br />\n咁就carry左佢3場😂 <br />\n因為呢個AC個條友 係我用劫之前<br />\n佢既戰績真係冇眼睇😂咁我相信佢應該新手黎😂<br />\n所以佢個fd突然問我<br />\n喂 你幾時練到隻劫咁勁嫁 收收埋埋 <br />\n下次攞出黎carry我地啦<br />\n下面有圖 我唔開LoL名啦 尊重番佢<br />\n如果有咩得罪 唔好見怪 我冇用你D點數嫁 <br />\n只係幫你升專7渣😂 <br />\n劫神到此一遊🤣🤣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NjVCGvy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNjVCGvy.png&h=46810ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TZKPxCe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTZKPxCe.png&h=869433bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ywtQg3V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FywtQg3V.png&h=822f2b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/14/031559_477bc03d4a485abb02a1638086dfe757.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F14%2F031559_477bc03d4a485abb02a1638086dfe757.png&h=73658912&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c44b3be24ca827867d7b02c5fcaeff1bc3ff4ca","tid":1020703,"uid":53170,"like":602,"dislike":5,"score":597,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T19:26:43.000Z","msg":"Lihkg = Facebook"},{"pid":"c43a76ceec194d49911783bb09ade3fabeae4f68","tid":1020703,"uid":105287,"like":405,"dislike":2,"score":403,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T19:28:27.000Z","msg":"挽你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" cla